Dear <%= @order.billing_address.full_name %>,

Thank you for your order at Mad Racing MX! Here are the details.
You can always view your full order details at http://madracingmx.com/orders/<%= @order.id %>

Order Reference Number: <%= @order.id %>

<% for order_item in @order.order_items -%>
<% if order_item.product_option_vehicle_model_id -%>
<% option_string = order_item.product_option_vehicle_model.vehicle_model.name + ' ' + order_item.product_option_vehicle_model.year_begin.to_s + '-' + order_item.product_option_vehicle_model.year_end.to_s -%>
<% elsif !order_item.product_option.name.blank? -%>
<% option_string =  order_item.product_option.name -%>
<% else -%>
<% option_string =  order_item.product_option.id.to_s -%>
<% end -%>
<%= order_item.quantity.to_s + ' x ' + order_item.product_option.product.name + ' (' + option_string + ')' %>
<% end -%>

Shipping Address

<%= @order.shipping_address.full_name %>
<%= @order.shipping_address.address_1 %>
<% unless @order.shipping_address.address_2.blank? -%>
<%= @order.shipping_address.address_2 %>
<% end -%>
<%= @order.shipping_address.city %>
<%= @order.shipping_address.state %>
<%= @order.shipping_address.zipcode %>

Thank you!
Mad Racing MX

